4.2.1 The measurement of macroeconomic performance
4.2.1.1–4.2.1.3 (Same as AS)

4.2.1.4 Uses of national income data

Use and limitations to assess changes in living standards over time
Use and limitations to compare living standards between countries
Importance of purchasing power parity (PPP) exchange rates
