4.2.2.1–4.2.2.2 (Same as AS)

4.2.2.3 The determinants of aggregate demand (Same as AS)

4.2.2.4 Aggregate demand and the level of economic activity (As AS, plus:)

Concept of marginal propensity to consume (MPC)
